user Stories
1. As a user, I want to view all countries sorted by population.
2. As a user, I want to view all cities sorted by population.
3. As a user, I want to see the top N populated countries/cities.
4. As a user, I want to generate population reports.
5. As a user, I want to fetch language speaker statistics.

 Tasks Breakdown
Set up database connection in C#.
Implement SQL queries for population sorting.
Develop API endpoints for fetching data.
Create a user interface to display reports.
Write unit tests to validate results.
